{"tid":1624712,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實美心元氣都冇想像中咁壞","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T06:58:09.000Z","uid":120538,"like":24,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"29db9b306e732ce28aa7fc9e89dadc1e25f175f2","tid":1624712,"uid":120538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:39:31.000Z","msg":"單純係個人立場，但點解咁講，因為去元氣幫襯過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">任食幾個鐘然後埋單$0.00。</span><br />\n<br />\n我想帶出嘅重點係，全店所有人都係呢個價錢呢個待遇，但係間野冇選擇落閂唔做生意。（仆街睇下福建360落閘報警CLS）<br />\n<br />\n然後上網睇過好多間都係咁，咁即係管理層默認咗唔反對大家咁做。佢冇為我地出聲，但至少冇出賣我地（個條賣港大小姐例外！！！）<br />\n<br />\n我只係諗有咁多間野比人裝修完之後，但呢個集團仲係冇改變過呢個任你坐「漏洞」。可能佢係亀縮，但至少唔算係黑心。<br />\n<br />\n最後我想帶出一個重點，美心係本土餐飲集團，就好似泰咁，如果冇就佢，我地以後就可能好似其他行業咁，得返共產集團！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似買書咁...........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全部姓<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黨</span><br />\n<br />\n重點得一樣：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權</span></span>，我地需要更多力量同埋支持，本土勢力除左誠哥仲有呢d本土集團一樣重要。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n香港人 反抗</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd1adc5fc512cbec252409009b2c8635a76bc55","tid":1624712,"uid":120538,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0